<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.3">
<l>ēṟaṉaip pūvaṉaip pūmaka ṭaṉṉai</l>
<l>vēṟiṉṟi viṇṭoḻat taṉṉuḷ vaittu</l>
<l>mēṟaṉṉai mītiṭa nimirntumaṇ koṇṭa</l>
<l>māṟaṉiṉ mikkumōr tēvu muḷatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is there any god more than Māl</l>
<l>who took the earth by stretching [himself] out so that he placed himself above the highest [point],</l>
<l>putting inside himself, while heaven worships nothing else,</l>
<l>the one on the bull, the one in the flower [and] the lady of the flower.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
